{"tid":340732,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★不堪工作壓力，70後墮樓亡！","createTime":"2017-07-30T07:55:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-17T09:23:32.000Z","uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"7fa252f9ecabac72c8c117da8e1ef98d45aeed6c","tid":340732,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T07:55:35.000Z","msg":"黃埔新邨永富樓男子墮樓亡。上午11時許，姓李(38歲)男子走到大廈天台危險位置危坐，有住客發現立即報警。消防及救護員趕至現場進行游說，惟李突然飛墮平台，昏迷倒臥血泊中，被救下送院不治。現場未檢獲遺書，警方初步相信事件無可疑，惟死因有待驗屍後確定。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，死者有情緒病紀錄，在酒樓任職，曾透露有工作壓力不開心，近日亦曾與家人爭執。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170730/bkn-20170730122713790-0730_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170730%2Fbkn-20170730122713790-0730_00822_001.html&d=AT6lbvV0ajZKnYXeFQ9HRzOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=1f982d15\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170730/bkn-20170730122713790-0730_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"5183d963909c5f62f1f8443e6c72adfff1436a75","tid":340732,"uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T07:56:02.000Z","msg":"工作，不了！"},{"pid":"03c57b1eef0f77742a388eb02ff137edec4a5646","tid":340732,"uid":26752,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T08:21:01.000Z","msg":"依加d 70後真係唔唔捱得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有勇氣自殺，點解冇勇氣面對<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n辦法總比困難多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"426797607a24c4f78cc42c201bb5ecfcc5b35190","tid":340732,"uid":22047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T08:25:24.000Z","msg":"呢家70後都冇D獅子山精神<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"acbb450baec27bd88c67d0675f955ef0f4bf4ddc","tid":340732,"uid":19454,"like":1,"